15:9 Ariko akora ibyangwa n'Uwiteka nk'uko ba sekuruza bakoraga, ntiyareka ibyaha bya Yerobowamu mwene Nebati woheje Abisirayeli ngo bacumure.
15:10 Bukeye Shalumu mwene Yabeshi aramugomera, aramukubita amutsinda imbere ya rubanda, yima mu cyimbo cye.
15:11 Nuko indi mirimo ya Zekariya yanditswe mu gitabo cy'ibyo ku ngoma z'abami b'Abisirayeli.
15:12   Iryo ni ryo jambo Uwiteka yabwiye Yehu ati “Abana bawe kugeza ku buvivi bazicara ku ntebe y'ubwami bw'Abisirayeli.” Nuko birasohora.
15:13 Mu mwaka wa mirongo itatu n'icyenda wo ku ngoma ya Uziya umwami w'Abayuda, Shalumu mwene Yabeshi yarimye, amara ukwezi kumwe i Samariya ari ku ngoma.
15:14 Hanyuma Menahemu mwene Gadi ava i Tirusa arazamuka ajya i Samariya, yicirayo Shalumu mwene Yabeshi. Amaze kumwica yima mu cyimbo cye.
15:15 Nuko indi mirimo ya Shalumu n'ubugome bwe byanditswe mu gitabo cy'ibyo ku ngoma z'abami b'Abisirayeli.
15:16 Bukeye Menahemu ava i Tirusa atera i Tipusa, ahatsindana n'abari barimo bose n'ibihugu byaho. Icyatumye ahatsinda, ni uko banze kumwugururira amarembo, maze abagore batwite bari barimo bose arabafomoza.
15:17 Mu mwaka wa mirongo itatu n'icyenda wo ku ngoma ya Uziya umwami w'Abayuda, Menahemu mwene Gadi yimye muri Isirayeli, amara imyaka cumi i Samariya ari ku ngoma.
15:18 Ariko akora ibyangwa n'Uwiteka. Mu gihe yari akiriho, ntiyaretse ibyaha bya Yerobowamu mwene Nebati woheje Abisirayeli ngo bacumure.
15:19 Bukeye Puli umwami wa Ashuri atera igihugu. Menahemu ni ko guhongera Puli italanto z'ifeza igihumbi, kugira ngo amutize amaboko abone uko akomera mu bwami bwe.
15:20 Kandi Menahemu yari yatse abakomeye mu Bisirayeli b'abatunzi bose ifeza, umuntu wese muri bo yamwatse shekeli z'ifeza mirongo itanu, ngo azihe umwami wa Ashuri. Nuko umwami wa Ashuri arakimirana ntiyaguma muri icyo gihugu.
15:21 Nuko indi mirimo ya Menahemu n'ibyo yakoze byose, mbese ntibyanditswe mu gitabo cy'ibyo ku ngoma z'abami b'Abisirayeli?
