15:24 Ariko akora ibyangwa n'Uwiteka, ntiyareka ibyaha bya Yerobowamu mwene Nebati woheje Abisirayeli ngo bacumure.
15:25 Bukeye Peka mwene Remaliya umutware we aramugomera, amwicana na Arugobu na Ariyeha i Samariya, mu nzu y'igihome yo mu rugo rw'ibwami. Yari kumwe n'Abanyagaleyadi mirongo itanu, nuko amaze kumwica yima mu cyimbo cye.
15:26 Ariko indi mirimo ya Pekahiya n'ibyo yakoze byose, byanditswe mu gitabo cy'ibyo ku ngoma z'abami b'Abisirayeli.
15:27 Mu mwaka wa mirongo itanu n'ibiri wo ku ngoma ya Uziya umwami w'Abayuda, Peka mwene Remaliya yimye muri Isirayeli i Samariya, amara imyaka makumyabiri ari ku ngoma.
15:28 Ariko akora ibyangwa n'Uwiteka, ntiyareka ibyaha bya Yerobowamu mwene Nebati woheje Abisirayeli ngo bacumure.
